BORNEO NEEDS (AS MINIMUM):
--------------------------

-Basic right-click mouse events.
-Have tabs to surf the web.
-.dekstop and other files for an installation in a Linux/BSD system (or *NIX in general).
-The "stop charge" button must be hide if the page is loaded.
-A little drop window in  top left corner to see the URL when mouse is over a link.
-Possibility to create a new window only for private browse mode.
-History and bookmarks.
-A download manager.
-An adblock system.
-Good HTML5 and WebGL if is possible compatibility.
